'Ohana means family. ❤️ We are celebrating the upcoming live-action release of Disney’s Lilo & Stitch, landing in theaters May 23, with playful new looks in the skies. Starting today you can spot Stitch striking his best Pualani profile on Hawaiian’s Airbus A330, the first of three specially designed aircraft. Can you guess what the next two will look like? Comment below! 

